-This disc contains the polished studio demos that the Jersey Boys took with them to the studio to begin recording the epic Slippery When Wet with their producer. All are different from the final version and are fun to listen to with decent audio quality.

For those of you only wanting the good studio demos, Sessions 5/8/9/10/11 are the best, so look out for them!
